.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-KEYSEND" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-keysend \- send a spontaneous keysend payment
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-keysend
.I node_id
.I amount_msat
.RI [ label ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sends a spontaneous (keysend) payment to
.I node_id
for
.I amount_msat
without a prior invoice.
Uses
.BR "lightning-cli keysend" .
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{payment_hash, status, amount_msat, destination}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-send (1),
.BR lightning-payment-status (1)
